description:
Dempsey Williamson Young Kelly & Hertel, established in 1849, is one of Wisconsin's oldest continuously operated law firms. Since its beginning, Dempsey Law has always provided the highest quality legal services in a skillful and efficient manner. Located in Oshkosh, we are a full service law firm comprised of skillful Wisconsin trial lawyers and experienced general practitioners representing individuals in matters such as personal injury or family law . In addition, we represent a broad array of financial, commercial, banking, service, manufacturing, publishing, educational, charitable and municipal enterprises throughout Wisconsin. Whether providing legal services in large or small matters, we are committed to and have a proud tradition of providing sophisticated, creative and practical solutions to our client's problems on a cost effective basis.

Wisconsin Personal Injury Lawyers and So Much More

In addition to Dempsey Law's personal injury and family law practice , we have an expansive and well-established traditional practice. Today, Dempsey Law is truly a comprehensive full service 9-attorney law firm serving all of the Fox Valley and east-central Wisconsin in the areas of:

Personal injury law, including car accidents
Medical malpractice
Products liability
Family law, including divorce, custody and support
Business and commercial law, including corporate formation, commercial/banking transactions, and real estate
Tax, estate planning and probate
No matter what the legal need, our accomplished team of trial and general practice lawyers can help you get the results you are looking for. From our offices in Oshkosh, we serve Winnebago, Outagamie, Brown, Calumet, Fond du Lac, Sheboygan and Manitowoc counties, including the communities of Green Bay, Appleton, Neenah, Menasha, Fond du Lac and Winneconne. We offer a free initial consultation. On personal injury matters , there is no fee if we don't recover for you. Contact us today.
